{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775840917181,"sessionID":"ses_287a250eaffeEunusok4Vftxf0","part":{"id":"prt_d785de59e001R8toNTwbszu3jS","messageID":"msg_d785dcfd2001AewwIZv6MJE4nz","sessionID":"ses_287a250eaffeEunusok4Vftxf0","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_305fbcb1068844839ec56d27","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-003/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-003/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-003 — CRD 共享类型与常量 Tasks\n2: \n3: **Module:** pkg/apis  \n4: **Language:** Go  \n5: **Size:** S  \n6: **Stage:** ST-3 (Design completed)\n7: \n8: ---\n9: \n10: ## Phase 1: Directory Scaffold\n11: \n12: - [ ] **1.1** Create `pkg/apis/runtime/` directory (if not exists from AR-001)\n13: - [ ] **1.2** Create `pkg/apis/runtime/constants.go` - define shared constants\n14: - [ ] **1.3** Create `pkg/apis/runtime/types.go` - define shared types\n15: - [ ] **1.4** Create `pkg/apis/runtime/doc.go` - add Go package documentation\n16: \n17: ---\n18: \n19: ## Phase 2: Shared Constants\n20: \n21: - [ ] **2.1** Define final version label key: `AgentCubeVersionLabel = \"agentcube.io/version\"`\n22: - [ ] **2.2** Define final managed by label key: `AgentCubeManagedByLabel = \"agentcube.io/managed-by\"`\n23: - [ ] **2.3** Define runtime class label key: `RuntimeClassLabel = \"runtime.agentcube.io/class\"`\n24: - [ ] **2.4** Define sandbox annotation prefix: `SandboxAnnotationPrefix = \"sandbox.agentcube.io/\"`\n25: - [ ] **2.5** Define resource quota annotation: `ResourceQuotaAnnotation = \"resources.agentcube.io/quota\"`\n26: - [ ] **2.6** Define finalizer for runtime cleanup: `RuntimeFinalizer = \"agentcube.io/runtime-cleanup\"`\n27: - [ ] **2.7** Define default container image constants (e.g., `DefaultRuntimeImage`, `DefaultCodeInterpreterImage`)\n28: - [ ] **2.8** Define default resource values (e.g., `DefaultCPURequest`, `DefaultMemoryRequest`)\n29: \n30: ---\n31: \n32: ## Phase 3: Shared Types\n33: \n34: - [ ] **3.1** Define `ResourceQuota` type (if not already in v1alpha1/types.go)\n35: - [ ] **3.2** Define `NetworkPolicy` type (if not already in v1alpha1/types.go)\n36: - [ ] **3.3** Define `NetworkRule` type (if not already in v1alpha1/types.go)\n37: - [ ] **3.4** Define `LifecycleHook` type (if not already in v1alpha1/types.go)\n38: - [ ] **3.5** Define `CodeInterpreterSpec` type (if not already in v1alpha1/types.go)\n39: - [ ] **3.6** Add JSON tags (camelCase) and protobuf tags to all shared types\n40: - [ ] **3.7** Ensure types implement `runtime.Object` interface if needed\n41: \n42: ---\n43: \n44: ## Phase 4: Utility Functions\n45: \n46: - [ ] **4.1** Create `pkg/apis/runtime/helpers.go`\n47: - [ ] **4.2** Implement `GetSandboxName(runtimeName string) string` - generate sandbox pod name from runtime name\n48: - [ ] **4.3** Implement `GetSandboxLabels(runtimeName, version string) map[string]string` - generate standard labels for sandbox\n49: - [ ] **4.4** Implement `GetResourceQuotaFromAnnotation(annotations map[string]string) (*ResourceQuota, error)` - parse quota from annotation\n50: - [ ] **4.5** Implement `SetResourceQuotaAnnotation(annotations map[string]string, quota *ResourceQuota) error` - set quota annotation\n51: - [ ] **4.6** Implement `IsRuntimeTerminating(phase AgentRuntimePhase) bool` - check if runtime is in terminating state\n52: - [ ] **4.7** Implement `GetCondition(status *AgentRuntimeStatus, conditionType AgentRuntimeConditionType) *AgentRuntimeCondition` - get condition from status\n53: - [ ] **4.8** Implement `SetCondition(status *AgentRuntimeStatus, condition AgentRuntimeCondition)` - set or update condition in status\n54: \n55: ---\n56: \n57: ## Phase 5: Unit Tests\n58: \n59: - [ ] **5.1** Create `pkg/apis/runtime/constants_test.go`\n60: - [ ] **5.2** Test constant values are correct (non-empty, proper format)\n61: - [ ] **5.3** Create `pkg/apis/runtime/helpers_test.go`\n62: - [ ] **5.4** Test `GetSandboxName` generates valid Kubernetes names\n63: - [ ] **5.5** Test `GetSandboxLabels` returns expected label set\n64: - [ ] **5.6** Test `GetResourceQuotaFromAnnotation` with valid JSON\n65: - [ ] **5.7** Test `GetResourceQuotaFromAnnotation` with invalid JSON returns error\n66: - [ ] **5.8** Test `SetResourceQuotaAnnotation` sets correct annotation value\n67: - [ ] **5.9** Test `IsRuntimeTerminating` for all phases\n68: - [ ] **5.10** Test `GetCondition` returns nil for missing condition\n69: - [ ] **5.11** Test `GetCondition` returns correct condition when present\n70: - [ ] **5.12** Test `SetCondition` adds new condition\n71: - [ ] **5.13** Test `SetCondition` updates existing condition\n72: \n73: ---\n74: \n75: ## Phase 6: Integration & Verification\n76: \n77: - [ ] **6.1** Run `make test` - all unit tests pass\n78: - [ ] **6.2** Verify `pkg/apis/runtime` compiles without errors\n79: - [ ] **6.3** Verify constants are accessible from `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` package\n80: - [ ] **6.4** Verify shared types can be imported and used in v1alpha1 package\n81: - [ ] **6.5** Run `go test ./pkg/apis/runtime/...` with ≥80% coverage\n82: - [ ] **6.6** Verify helper functions work correctly with types from AR-001\n83: \n84: ---\n85: \n86: ## Verification Checklist\n87: \n88: - [ ] All Go code compiles without errors\n89: - [ ] `go test ./pkg/apis/runtime/...` passes with ≥80% coverage\n90: - [ ] Constants follow Kubernetes naming conventions\n91: - [ ] Shared types are properly documented with Go comments\n92: - [ ] Helper functions have comprehensive test coverage\n93: - [ ] No circular dependencies between `pkg/apis/runtime` and `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1`\n94: \n95: ---\n96: \n97: ## Dependencies\n98: \n99: | Task | Depends On |\n100: |------|------------|\n101: | Phase 2 | Phase 1 |\n102: | Phase 3 | Phase 1 |\n103: | Phase 4 | Phase 2, 3 |\n104: | Phase 5 | Phase 2, 3, 4 |\n105: | Phase 6 | Phase 4, 5 |\n106: \n107: ---\n108: \n109: ## References\n110: \n111: - Proposal: `changes/AR-003/proposal.md`\n112: - Related: `changes/AR-001/` (AgentRuntime CRD)\n113: - Related: `changes/AR-002/` (CodeInterpreter CRD)\n114: - API Conventions: `https://git.k8s.io/community/contributors/devel/sig-architecture/api-conventions.md`\n115: - Kubernetes Labels & Annotations: `https://kubernetes.io/docs/concepts/overview/working-with-objects/labels/`\n\n(End of file - total 115 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-003 — CRD 共享类型与常量 Tasks\n\n**Module:** pkg/apis  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** S  \n**Stage:** ST-3 (Design completed)\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1: Directory Scaffold\n\n- [ ] **1.1** Create `pkg/apis/runtime/` directory (if not exists from AR-001)\n- [ ] **1.2** Create `pkg/apis/runtime/constants.go` - define shared constants\n- [ ] **1.3** Create `pkg/apis/runtime/types.go` - define shared types\n- [ ] **1.4** Create `pkg/apis/runtime/doc.go` - add Go package documentation\n\n---\n\n## Phase 2: Shared Constants\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-003/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775840917118,"end":1775840917177}}}}
