{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775840941114,"sessionID":"ses_287a250eaffeEunusok4Vftxf0","part":{"id":"prt_d785e4f3d001e7c4D8zCdX0WVy","messageID":"msg_d785e3f70001kLt3w7bnROpBXT","sessionID":"ses_287a250eaffeEunusok4Vftxf0","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_9d362a77b4544cb39cfb5c7e","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-001/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-001/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义 Tasks\n2: \n3: **Module:** pkg/apis  \n4: **Language:** Go  \n5: **Size:** S  \n6: **Stage:** ST-3 (Design completed)\n7: \n8: ---\n9: \n10: ## Phase 1: Scaffold & Registration\n11: \n12: - [ ] **1.1** Create `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` directory structure\n13: - [ ] **1.2** Create `pkg/apis/runtime/register.go` - register API group\n14: - [ ] **1.3** Create `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go` - define `SchemeGroupVersion`, `SchemeBuilder`, `AddToScheme`\n15: - [ ] **1.4** Create `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/doc.go` - add Go package documentation\n16: \n17: ---\n18: \n19: ## Phase 2: Type Definitions\n20: \n21: - [ ] **2.1** Define `AgentRuntimePhase` enum (Pending, Running, Failed, Terminating)\n22: - [ ] **2.2** Define `AgentRuntimeCondition` struct (type, status, reason, message, lastTransitionTime)\n23: - [ ] **2.3** Define `CodeInterpreterSpec` struct (enabled, image, resources)\n24: - [ ] **2.4** Define `ResourceQuota` struct (cpu, memory, storage limits)\n25: - [ ] **2.5** Define `NetworkPolicy` struct (egressRules, ingressRules)\n26: - [ ] **2.6** Define `LifecycleHook` struct (preStart, postStop handlers)\n27: - [ ] **2.7** Define `AgentRuntimeSpec` struct (container, resources, network, lifecycle, codeInterpreter)\n28: - [ ] **2.8** Define `AgentRuntimeStatus` struct (phase, conditions, sandboxRef, startTime, lastTransitionTime)\n29: - [ ] **2.9** Define `AgentRuntime` struct (TypeMeta, ObjectMeta, Spec, Status)\n30: - [ ] **2.10** Define `AgentRuntimeList` struct (TypeMeta, ListMeta, Items)\n31: - [ ] **2.11** Add JSON tags (camelCase) and protobuf tags to all types\n32: - [ ] **2.12** Implement `runtime.Object` interface for AgentRuntime and AgentRuntimeList\n33: \n34: ---\n35: \n36: ## Phase 3: Defaults & Validation\n37: \n38: - [ ] **3.1** Create `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/defaults.go`\n39: - [ ] **3.2** Implement `SetDefaults_AgentRuntime` - set default phase to Pending, default resources if unspecified\n40: - [ ] **3.3** Create `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/validation.go`\n41: - [ ] **3.4** Implement `ValidateAgentRuntime` - validate spec fields (resource values, image format, hook URLs)\n42: - [ ] **3.5** Implement `ValidateAgentRuntimeStatusUpdate` - validate status transitions and field immutability\n43: \n44: ---\n45: \n46: ## Phase 4: CRD Manifest Generation\n47: \n48: - [ ] **4.1** Add `+genclient` and `+k8s:deepcopy-gen` markers to type definitions\n49: - [ ] **4.2** Add `+kubebuilder:object:root=true` and `+kubebuilder:subresource:status` markers\n50: - [ ] **4.3** Add `+kubebuilder:printcolumn` markers for kubectl output (NAME, PHASE, SANDBOX, AGE)\n51: - [ ] **4.4** Run `make gen-crd` (controller-gen) to generate CRD YAML\n52: - [ ] **4.5** Verify generated manifest at `manifests/charts/base/crds/agentruntime.yaml`\n53: - [ ] **4.6** Validate OpenAPI v3 schema in generated CRD\n54: \n55: ---\n56: \n57: ## Phase 5: Client Code Generation\n58: \n59: - [ ] **5.1** Update `hack/boilerplate.go.txt` if needed\n60: - [ ] **5.2** Update `hack/update-codegen.sh` with API group info\n61: - [ ] **5.3** Run `make gen-client` to generate clientset, listers, informers\n62: - [ ] **5.4** Verify generated code compiles: `pkg/client/clientset/versioned/`\n63: - [ ] **5.5** Verify generated code compiles: `pkg/client/listers/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n64: - [ ] **5.6** Verify generated code compiles: `pkg/client/informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n65: \n66: ---\n67: \n68: ## Phase 6: Unit Tests\n69: \n70: - [ ] **6.1** Create `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types_test.go`\n71: - [ ] **6.2** Test type round-trip serialization (Go → JSON → Go)\n72: - [ ] **6.3** Test `SetDefaults_AgentRuntime` behavior\n73: - [ ] **6.4** Create `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/validation_test.go`\n74: - [ ] **6.5** Test valid AgentRuntime specs pass validation\n75: - [ ] **6.6** Test invalid specs fail validation (negative resources, invalid image names)\n76: - [ ] **6.7** Test status update validation (phase transitions, immutable fields)\n77: - [ ] **6.8** Test `AddToScheme` registration works correctly\n78: \n79: ---\n80: \n81: ## Phase 7: Integration & Verification\n82: \n83: - [ ] **7.1** Run `make test` - all unit tests pass\n84: - [ ] **7.2** Run `make verify` - code generation is up to date\n85: - [ ] **7.3** Apply CRD to test cluster: `kubectl apply -f manifests/charts/base/crds/agentruntime.yaml`\n86: - [ ] **7.4** Verify `kubectl get agentruntime` shows custom columns\n87: - [ ] **7.5** Create sample AgentRuntime YAML in `examples/agentruntime.yaml`\n88: - [ ] **7.6** Apply sample and verify resource is created\n89: - [ ] **7.7** Verify Go client can create/get/update AgentRuntime resources\n90: \n91: ---\n92: \n93: ## Verification Checklist\n94: \n95: - [ ] All Go code compiles without errors\n96: - [ ] `go test ./pkg/apis/runtime/...` passes with ≥80% coverage\n97: - [ ] CRD manifest validates with `kubeval` or `kubectl --dry-run=server`\n98: - [ ] Generated client code is up to date (`git diff` shows no changes after `make gen-client`)\n99: - [ ] Example YAML applies successfully to test cluster\n100: \n101: ---\n102: \n103: ## Dependencies\n104: \n105: | Task | Depends On |\n106: |------|------------|\n107: | Phase 2 | Phase 1 |\n108: | Phase 3 | Phase 2 |\n109: | Phase 4 | Phase 2 |\n110: | Phase 5 | Phase 4 |\n111: | Phase 6 | Phase 2, 3 |\n112: | Phase 7 | Phase 4, 5, 6 |\n113: \n114: ---\n115: \n116: ## References\n117: \n118: - Proposal: `changes/AR-001/proposal.md`\n119: - Implementation Plan: `proposal.md#implementation-plan`\n120: - Success Criteria: `proposal.md#success-criteria`\n121: - API Conventions: `https://git.k8s.io/community/contributors/devel/sig-architecture/api-conventions.md`\n\n(End of file - total 121 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义 Tasks\n\n**Module:** pkg/apis  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** S  \n**Stage:** ST-3 (Design completed)\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1: Scaffold & Registration\n\n- [ ] **1.1** Create `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` directory structure\n- [ ] **1.2** Create `pkg/apis/runtime/register.go` - register API group\n- [ ] **1.3** Create `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go` - define `SchemeGroupVersion`, `SchemeBuilder`, `AddToScheme`\n- [ ] **1.4** Create `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/doc.go` - add Go package documentation\n\n---\n\n## Phase 2: Type Definitions\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-001/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775840941104,"end":1775840941112}}}}
