{"type":"text","timestamp":1775840954536,"sessionID":"ses_287a250eaffeEunusok4Vftxf0","part":{"id":"prt_d785e6783001rR3qYqTj6zJem6","messageID":"msg_d785e546a0014QQNYiusAIWQpz","sessionID":"ses_287a250eaffeEunusok4Vftxf0","type":"text","text":"Based on my analysis of the AR-003 tasks and current implementation state:\n\n## AR-003 — CRD 共享类型与常量 Archive Summary\n\n### Completed ✓\n\n**Shared Types (in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go`):**\n- `ResourceQuota` - resource limits/requests type\n- `NetworkPolicy` - network access rules type\n- `NetworkRule` - single network rule type\n- `LifecycleHook` - lifecycle callbacks type\n- `ContainerSpec` - container configuration type\n- `CodeInterpreterSpec` - embedded code interpreter config\n- `AgentRuntimeCondition` - reusable status condition pattern\n- `AgentRuntimePhase` enum (Pending, Running, Failed, Terminating)\n- `AgentRuntimeConditionType` enum (Ready, SandboxCreated, CodeInterpreterReady)\n\n**CRD Registration:**\n- `pkg/apis/runtime/register.go` - API group registration\n- `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go` - Scheme registration\n- Full CRD type definitions with JSON/protobuf tags\n\n### Deferred ⏸️\n\n**Shared Constants (not implemented):**\n- Label keys (`AgentCubeVersionLabel`, `AgentCubeManagedByLabel`, `RuntimeClassLabel`)\n- Annotation prefixes (`SandboxAnnotationPrefix`, `ResourceQuotaAnnotation`)\n- Finalizers (`RuntimeFinalizer`)\n- Default values (`DefaultRuntimeImage`, `DefaultCPURequest`, etc.)\n\n**Utility Functions (not implemented):**\n- `GetSandboxName()` - generate sandbox pod names\n- `GetSandboxLabels()` - generate standard labels\n- `GetResourceQuotaFromAnnotation()` / `SetResourceQuotaAnnotation()` - quota parsing\n- `IsRuntimeTerminating()` - phase check helper\n- `GetCondition()` / `SetCondition()` - status condition helpers\n\n**Unit Tests:**\n- No dedicated tests for constants or helper functions\n\n**Reason:** AR-003 was partially merged into AR-001 - the shared types were defined directly in `v1alpha1/types.go` rather than being separated into a dedicated `runtime` package. The constants and helpers were deferred pending actual controller implementation needs.","time":{"start":1775840954534,"end":1775840954534}}}
